FreeRTOS下的移植基本同裸机的配置相差不大，也就需要改个时基，使用FreeRTOS的
时基配置lv_conf.h中添加自定义时基
bash
/*Use a custom tick source that tells the elapsed time in milliseconds.
 *It removes the need to manually update the tick with `lv_tick_inc()`)*/
#define LV_TICK_CUSTOM 1 //使能1，默认是0
#if LV_TICK_CUSTOM
    #define LV_TICK_CUSTOM_INCLUDE &quot;FreeRTOS.h&quot;         /*Header for the system time function*/
    #define LV_TICK_CUSTOM_SYS_TIME_EXPR (xTaskGetTickCount())    /*Expression evaluating to current system time in ms*/
注意该配置与裸机移植的配置不能兼容。
